{"tid":1294574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(長期人手置頂)叮囑各界人仕  如若被捕  請立即除衫","createTime":"2019-07-07T20:06:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T10:28:46.000Z","uid":144865,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"810283d0570238256ff07432380ec30a55da9bc1","tid":1294574,"uid":144865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T20:06:25.000Z","msg":"今日睇果燃live見到有人被警察拘捕，記者話佢當刻已經拍攝到有警司級向疑犯用手扯頭，記者表示相信疑犯上到車後命途一定不保。<br />\n  <br />\n  而事實，該名疑犯上車後，警察拉埋窗簾，令記者唔能夠了解車內狀況。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">若果你見到傳媒之前，已經比警方已不合法武力對待，請於可行情況下，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一見到傳媒，立即展示傷勢</span></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>若果你怕保釋後得番半條人命，請立即向當時傳媒展示你現時身體情況。及後，踏出警局時亦<span style=\"color: red;\">請立即聯絡傳媒并將任何不合理對待及傷勢展示。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住:要傷，都唔好喺和理非時傷。唔好浪費自己每一滴血</span></span>"},{"pid":"d563272f385ed8e6dcce4d683f1b4356bafa7d31","tid":1294574,"uid":31762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T20:22:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9418bd77559b73d41aa9619e578688ae8b259fa","tid":1294574,"uid":144865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T21:48:20.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"2263c08a80d2100a61e7cd2738db35295bd6c86c","tid":1294574,"uid":144865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T22:50:44.000Z","msg":"推，救得一個得一個"},{"pid":"997c148103a453d72ed8afa9f2f878da675a457a","tid":1294574,"uid":243834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T23:43:22.000Z","msg":"推，除衫保平安"},{"pid":"a95329f00981872a36d61fbe31c61c992f39bf3a","tid":1294574,"uid":123969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T23:45:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />good idea"},{"pid":"a02f46d3691d456eb20080d7ad9c1aa7da2c5ae7","tid":1294574,"uid":263438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T23:51:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d51408866eec3e09e94de5eced15894ef3973fda","tid":1294574,"uid":261819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T23:54:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e4fea5b97ff2660db4d1a4d8499f8b61517f6a8e","tid":1294574,"uid":144865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T00:58:17.000Z","msg":"自推，無野講之餘再多重保障"},{"pid":"ae15d7e2df5469b1fcee850a857427095692a5ab","tid":1294574,"uid":144865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:28:46.000Z","msg":"推比多啲潛在受害者睇到"}]}